** Physics of the Lyalpha forest

  $ F_{\srm obs} = F_{\srm emit} e^{-\tau} $$
  where $\tau$ (the optical depth) is proportional to
  the density of neutral hydrogen

  #+latex: \newcommand\angle[1]{\left\langle#1\right\rangle}

  \begin{align}
  \delta F &= e^{-\delta \tau} - 1 \\
  \delta F &\equiv \frac{F_{\srm obs}}{\angle{F_{\srm obs}}} \equiv \frac{\tau}{\angle{\tau}}.
  \end{align}
  
  KG Lee puts out a catalog giving his best estimates of the continua


